---
title: Mexican Style Spiced Beef Loaded Buns with Mustardy Potato Salad and Rocket
description: These Mexican Style Spiced Beef Loaded Buns take only 25 minutes to make. Inspired by the flavours of Mexico, this spicy beef filling is piled into buns and topped with cheese for a quick but flavoursome meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W40_UK_QR21311-10_Main_low_2-f1e6e0de.jpg
